  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "IT Recruiter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience      in complete recruitment life cycle process starting from sourcing -      validating resumes, preliminary interviews, HR interviews, salary      negotiations, and rolling out offers.</li>\n  <li>Ability      to perform multiple tasks with the right prioritization</li>\n  <li>Ensure      all recruitment processes and activities remain compliant to Country      specific employment laws &amp; regulations</li>\n  <li>Good      experience in sourcing profiles using a mix of channels like web portals,      advertisements, walk-in, professional networking, personal references,      headhunting, and vendors.</li>\n  <li>Effective      utilization of the portals, referral methods, and other varied techniques      like headhunting and cold calling.</li>\n  <li>Must be      able to uphold and manage a good ‘Candidate experience’</li>\n  <li>Execute      and support recruitment and onboarding activities in a timely and      effective manner</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum      3- 6 years of experience in IT recruitment in Singapore. Staffing /      professional services experience is a must.</li>\n  <li>A      self-motivated, energetic, smart, and intelligent recruitment professional      aiming toward the best always</li>\n  <li>Excellent      communication &amp; interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Must be      a good Team player</li>\n  <li>Must be      able to work in an environment with high inter-dependencies between teams      and cross-cultural colleagues.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Other</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>IT      consulting experience.</li>\n  <li>CV      Submission target – should’ve done 2-3 submissions per day.</li>\n  <li>Joiner      target – minimum 2 per month.</li>\n  <li>Salary      – SGD 5500 per month base + incentives based on performance.</li>\n  <li>Open to      Singaporeans and Singapore PR.</li>\n</ul>",
